OL,3,GHighlands & Eilean Siar
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FIt will be a largely dry and
OL,6,Fbright day with some hazy sunshine at
OL,7,Ftimes but the odd light shower is
OL,8,Fpossible. Still warm in the east but
OL,9,Fnot as warm as recent days in the west.
OL,10,
OL,11,CTonight:FIt will be dry in the evening
OL,12,Fwith some brightness at first. It will
OL,13,Fbecome increasingly cloudy overnight
OL,14,Fwith some showery outbreaks of rain
OL,15,Fdeveloping.
OL,16,
OL,17,CSaturday:FIt will be cloudy throughout
OL,18,Fthe day with showery outbreaks of
OL,19,Frain, these turning heavy in places
OL,20,Fthrough the afternoon. Feeling much
OL,21,Fcooler than recent days.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
